sect2.para:
There are few points about wxBoolProperty that require further discussion:

wxBoolProperty can be shown as either normal combo box or as a check box. Property attribute wxPG_BOOL_USE_CHECKBOX is used to change this. For example, if you have a wxFlagsProperty, you can set its all items to use check box using the following: pg->SetPropertyAttribute("MyFlagsProperty",wxPG_BOOL_USE_CHECKBOX,true,wxPG_RECURSE);

Following will set all individual bool properties in your control to use check box:
